1 Description of DataSchema variable

The description of harmonised variables is the following:

  • Variable label: Has other (living) family members (e.g. parents, siblings, in-laws, etc.)

2.1.1.2 Harmonisation algorithm

To compute the harmonize variable from the study-specific variable it has to be recoded as follows:

  • if any eqauls 1 or disib>0 then 1
  • if all are equal 2 and disib=0 then 0
  • -1 into 996
  • -8 into 998
  • -9 into 997, but -9 for scfam into 995
  • NA into 999

R script:

ELSA_ds_w1 <- tibble(id = ELSA_w1_oth_fam$id)

ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib), "NA='-999'")

ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam <- c(NA)
for (i in 1:dim(ELSA_w1_oth_fam)[1]) {
    if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam[i] == 1 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == 1 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma[i] == 
        1 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib[i] > 0) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 1
    } else if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam[i] == 2 & ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa[i] %in% c(2, 
        -1) & ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma[i] %in% c(2, -1) & ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib[i] == 
        0) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 0
    } else if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -8 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -8 | 
        ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -8 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib[i] == -8) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 998
    } else if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -9 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -9 | 
        ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib[i] == -9) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 997
    } else if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -9) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 995
    } else if (ELSA_w1_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -1 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -1 | 
        ELSA_w1_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -1 | ELSA_w1_oth_fam$disib[i] == -1) {
        ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam[i] = 996
    }
}

ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam), "NA='999'")
ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam <- labelled(ELSA_ds_w1$oth_fam, labels = c(No = 0, Yes = 1, 
    Missing = 999, `Do not know` = 998, Refuse = 997, `Not applicable` = 996, 
    `Don't answer` = 995, `Not attempt/not done/not yet recorded` = 994, `disable to measure` = 993, 
    Impute = 992, `CAPI/interviewer error` = 991))

2.1.5.2 Harmonisation algorithm

To recode the harmonize variable from the study-specific variable it has to be recoded as follows:

  • if any eqauls 1 or disib>0 then 1
  • if all are equal 2 and disib=0 then 0
  • -1 or -2 into 996
  • -8 into 998
  • -9 into 997, but -9 for scfam into 995
  • NA into 999

R script:

ELSA_ds_w5 <- tibble(id = ELSA_w5_oth_fam$id)

ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma), "NA='-999'")
ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib <- car::recode(as.vector(ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib), "NA='-999'")

ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam <- c(NA)
for (i in 1:dim(ELSA_w5_oth_fam)[1]) {
    if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == 1 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == 1 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] == 
        1 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] > 0) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 1
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == 2 & ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] %in% c(2, 
        -1) & ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] %in% c(2, -1) & ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] == 
        0) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 0
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -8 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -8 | 
        ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -8 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] == -8) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 998
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -2 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -2 | 
        ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -2 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] == -2) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 996
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -9 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -9 | 
        ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] == -9) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 997
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -9) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 995
    } else if (ELSA_w5_oth_fam$scfam[i] == -1 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinfa[i] == -1 | 
        ELSA_w5_oth_fam$dinma[i] == -1 | ELSA_w5_oth_fam$disib[i] == -1) {
        ELSA_ds_w5$oth_fam[i] = 996
    }
}
